{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2013/09/fujiuyuan-outdoor-portrait/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/bts/","name":"镜头背后"}],"tags":[{"name":"人像","path":"/tag/portrait/"},{"name":"宜昌","path":"/tag/yichang/"},{"name":"室外","path":"/tag/outdoor/"},{"name":"房地产","path":"/tag/real-estate/"},{"name":"摄影","path":"/tag/photography/"},{"name":"花絮","path":"/tag/highlights/"},{"name":"香山福久源","path":"/tag/fujiuyuan/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/2013-08-31fujiuyuan.jpg"},"path":"/2013/09/fujiuyuan-outdoor-portrait/","date":"2013-09-02T23:29:13.000Z","excerpt":"8月31日，秋高气爽心情好，到位于宜昌伍家岗区桔城路的香山福久源一期小区拍摄外景人像。小区的坡地园林和坡地步道 … ","title":"香山福久源外景人像拍摄花絮","content":"<p>8月31日，秋高气爽心情好，到位于宜昌伍家岗区桔城路的香山福久源一期小区拍摄外景人像。小区的坡地园林和坡地步道景观比较不错，特别是步道鲜亮的色彩再加上水雾的渲染。</p>\n<p>感谢参与拍摄的望超、赵强和其他摄影师，模特程艳、陈启省、赵晓蕾，还有香山福久源马主任、宋主任的支持。</p>\n<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNjA0Mjk0Mjc2/v.swf\"/><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\"/><param name=\"quality\" value=\"high\"/><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"/><embed width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" src=\"//player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNjA0Mjk0Mjc2/v.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" quality=\"high\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"/></object></p>\n<p>首届香山福久源杯“我爱我家 最美香山福久源”摄影比赛正在进行中，欢迎社会各界摄影爱好者到小区拍摄，并将你精彩的作品投稿。需要小区物业配合、投稿或者需要模特请联系我。</p>\n<p><!--more--></p>\n<p>拍摄活动仍然比较慌乱，希望在以后的活动中能逐渐形成一支能互相配合进行拍摄的，分工明确的队伍，而不是一群拿照相机的摄影师。花絮短片，纯属娱乐。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/2013-08-31fujiuyuan.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"168\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1381\" alt=\"2013-08-31fujiuyuan\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/2013-08-31fujiuyuan-300x168.jpg\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/2013-08-31fujiuyuan-300x168.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/2013-08-31fujiuyuan-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/2013-08-31fujiuyuan.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2013/09/fujiuyuan-outdoor-portrait/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}